<s> p code CMModel /code is an abstract object that could map to a DTD, an XML Schema, a database schema, etc.  </s>
<s> It's a generalized content model object, that has both an internal and external subset.  </s>
<s> The internal subset would always exist, even if empty, with the external subset (if present) being represented as by an "active" code CMExternalModel /code .  </s>
<s> Many code CMExternalModel /code s could exist, but only one can be specified as "active"; it is also possible that none are "active".  </s>
<s> The issue of multiple content models is misleading since in this architecture, only one code CMModel /code exists, with an internal subset that references the external subset.  </s>
<s> If the external subset changes to another "acitve" code CMExternalModel /code , the internal subset is "fixed up."  </s>
